data.text:
1178 Aster Boulevard North West is a residence located in Edmonton, Alberta. It is situated in the community of Aster in Edmonton. Aster Boulevard has 2 postings currently for sale, while the district of Aster has 19 postings for sale. That's just 0.6% of the 3,161 total properties for sale in the city of Edmonton. The average asking price of a home in Aster is $519,378, with an estimated mortgage of $1,896 per month.* That is 1.2x the average list price of $423,472 in Edmonton. The average Aster listed property is 152 sq ft, has 3 beds, and 3 baths. The majority of available postings in the community around 1178 Aster Boulevard North West are houses. The 3 bed, 3 bath townhouse for sale at 1311 30 Av NW, Edmonton is comparable and listed at $419,900. Another similar home is the 3 bed, 3 bath townhouse located at 2145 28 St NW, Edmonton and priced for sale at $367,900.

* Monthly payments are an estimate based on a mortgage with 20% down @ 2.65% with a 5-yr Variable rate

Although this home is no longer listed, there are still 7 Aster townhouses on the market. In addition, there are 573 townhouses for sale in Edmonton.

The home at 1178 Aster Boulevard is a row / townhouse.
